They are suffering/People are watching/We are moving. 

Ukraine DAO is founded by HundredDAO, which aims to raise 100 ETH to help the people suffering from warfare in Ukraine. People donating more than 0.05 ETH will receive a HundredNFT as a souvenir of saving refugees in Ukraine.
